  "texts": [
    "This suspicion is onto something-at least insofar as these artifacts do not seem widespread among the general public.",
    "And yet, it seems that the (perhaps still few) people that actually use these artifacts can do so reliably.",
    "Chatbots such as Replikas are ever-available thanks to our smartphones.",
    "And, at least in fairly specific settings, affective robots might be reliably available too (Tanaka et al. 2015; Miyagawa et al. 2019).",
    "So, at least some artificial agents can (at least in principle) be reliably used, in a way that could engender an extension of our sense of self."
